it would kill our parents.

569
00:38:23,763 --> 00:38:24,602
Mother.

570
00:38:26,723 --> 00:38:28,203
Could you buy me

571
00:38:29,122 --> 00:38:31,122
bright red fabric?

572
00:38:35,203 --> 00:38:37,162
I want to embroider a wedding dress
for myself.

573
00:38:40,243 --> 00:38:43,403
Well, red color?

574
00:38:44,323 --> 00:38:45,323
I know.

575
00:38:46,042 --> 00:38:47,803
Only the rightful wife

576
00:38:48,363 --> 00:38:49,803
can wear a bright red dress.

577
00:38:50,522 --> 00:38:53,883
I just want to realize a wish.

578
00:38:57,243 --> 00:38:58,602
I'll buy it for you.

579
00:39:00,203 --> 00:39:01,243
Thank you.

580
00:39:03,243 --> 00:39:04,522
I have a headache.

581
00:39:05,602 --> 00:39:06,723
You may go.

582
00:39:07,883 --> 00:39:08,763
Rulan.

583
00:39:09,162 --> 00:39:10,283
Take a break.

584
00:39:13,042 --> 00:39:13,923
Well,

585
00:39:15,442 --> 00:39:16,923
you get some rest.

586
00:39:18,562 --> 00:39:20,243
Don't overthink.

587
00:39:21,883 --> 00:39:22,923
Be good.

588
00:40:57,042 --> 00:40:58,243
Meng Wan came to see you.

589
00:40:58,683 --> 00:41:01,042
You two can talk.

590
00:41:19,763 --> 00:41:21,403
Why did they lock you up?

591
00:41:21,923 --> 00:41:23,002
What happened?

592
00:41:23,803 --> 00:41:25,683
Were you discovered
when you tried to leave?

593
00:41:26,363 --> 00:41:27,122
It's okay.

594
00:41:27,403 --> 00:41:28,962
We can find another way.

595
00:41:29,642 --> 00:41:30,482
No.

596
00:41:31,562 --> 00:41:34,122
I didn't plan to leave.

597
00:41:37,243 --> 00:41:38,283
What's this?

598
00:41:40,002 --> 00:41:41,763
I'm embroidering a wedding dress
for myself.

599
00:41:43,442 --> 00:41:44,082
Why?

600
00:41:44,203 --> 00:41:45,602
Didn't we have a deal?

601
00:41:46,203 --> 00:41:49,243
We will wander the world together.

602
00:41:50,803 --> 00:41:53,162
It's just a joke.
Don't take it too seriously.

603
00:41:53,923 --> 00:41:55,482
We are women.

604
00:41:56,042 --> 00:41:57,562
How are we supposed to survive outside?

605
00:41:58,763 --> 00:41:59,763
By embroidery?

606
00:42:00,403 --> 00:42:01,283
Don't be silly.

607
00:42:01,883 --> 00:42:03,042
Where

608
00:42:04,843 --> 00:42:05,962
and how can we

609
00:42:06,203 --> 00:42:07,323
sell our embroidery?

610
00:42:07,642 --> 00:42:09,363
Even if we can barely make a living,

611
00:42:10,002 --> 00:42:12,442
what if we

612
00:42:12,883 --> 00:42:13,962
encounter bullies?

613
00:42:14,203 --> 00:42:15,442
There's always a way out.

614
00:42:15,642 --> 00:42:16,843
Don't give up.

615
00:42:17,522 --> 00:42:19,203
But I don't want to take risks anymore.

616
00:42:23,403 --> 00:42:24,683
Mrs. Wu is right.

617
00:42:24,962 --> 00:42:27,923
Perhaps marrying Wu Lian
is the best choice.

618
00:42:28,642 --> 00:42:30,683
