619
00:42:31,323 --> 00:42:33,923
Mrs. Wu is a lady of a good family.

620
00:42:34,363 --> 00:42:35,683
She won't give me a hard time.

621
00:42:37,042 --> 00:42:38,803
So I just need to live my life

622
00:42:38,962 --> 00:42:42,042
